# Configuration file for Hughes Power Watchdog integration
# This integration uses UI-based configuration flow through Home Assistant
# No YAML configuration is required or supported

# To configure:
# 1. Go to Settings -> Devices & Services in Home Assistant
# 2. Click "Add Integration"
# 3. Search for "Hughes Power Watchdog"
# 4. Follow the on-screen instructions

# Optional configuration (set via integration options):
# - scan_interval: Update interval in seconds (default: 30)
